1
00:00:10,480 --> 00:00:11,880
=The Quirky and The Charming=

2
00:01:19,180 --> 00:01:23,660
=Episode 11=

3
00:01:25,120 --> 00:01:27,480
You told him to make your bed,

4
00:01:27,720 --> 00:01:28,680
organize your clothes,

5
00:01:28,840 --> 00:01:30,600
and fill up your bathtub.

6
00:01:30,960 --> 00:01:33,080
You even wanted him
to wash your hair for you.

7
00:01:33,560 --> 00:01:34,760
And scrub your back as well.

8
00:01:37,360 --> 00:01:38,400
I'm done for.

9
00:01:38,840 --> 00:01:39,840
I'm dead meat.

10
00:01:40,480 --> 00:01:42,200
I'm sure he wants to kill me now.

11
00:01:43,240 --> 00:01:44,520
I don't think so.

12
00:01:44,880 --> 00:01:47,040
He seemed normal.

13
00:01:48,400 --> 00:01:50,080
I don't think it's normal.

14
00:01:51,080 --> 00:01:52,520
He didn't make a fuss.

15
00:01:52,880 --> 00:01:54,640
He did whatever you wanted him to do.

16
00:01:55,888 --> 00:01:57,600
- Is that normal?
- Is that normal?

17
00:02:01,160 --> 00:02:04,040
The calm before the storm
is always the quietest.

18
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:08,040
The quieter it is, the bigger the storm.

19
00:02:08,920 --> 00:02:11,160
Why didn't you guys stop me?

20
00:02:11,840 --> 00:02:13,520
Do you know how drunk you were?

21
00:02:13,640 --> 00:02:14,920
We couldn't stop you, you know?

22
00:02:15,080 --> 00:02:17,280
You didn't want to let go
of Vincent's thigh.

23
00:02:17,377 --> 00:02:19,333
I thought you were
going along with your plan.

24
00:02:19,720 --> 00:02:21,720
If Boss had his usual personality,

25
00:02:21,760 --> 00:02:23,680
he would've sent you packing.

26
00:02:24,080 --> 00:02:25,680
But now, he hasn't reacted yet.

27
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:27,280
What does that mean?

28
00:02:30,240 --> 00:02:32,240
That means he hasn't decided yet.

29
00:02:36,760 --> 00:02:37,920
Could it be...

30
00:02:41,640 --> 00:02:43,880
- You two!
- You two!

31
00:02:45,320 --> 00:02:46,680
Yi Ran, you're something else.

32
00:02:47,133 --> 00:02:48,860
You're playing hard-to-get
with Mr. Lin Jr.

33
00:02:48,866 --> 00:02:50,640
and flirting with Vincent
at the same time.

34
00:02:50,840 --> 00:02:53,040
You're occupying
two outstanding males at once.

35
00:02:53,200 --> 00:02:55,040
This is a huge waste of resources.

36
00:02:55,400 --> 00:02:56,920
What nonsense was that?

37
00:03:26,200 --> 00:03:26,720
Come in.

38
00:03:36,640 --> 00:03:37,360
Cut to the chase.

39
00:03:37,560 --> 00:03:38,320
I'm busy.

40
00:03:41,080 --> 00:03:42,400
Regarding last night,

41
00:03:44,844 --> 00:03:46,500
just treat it
as if nothing had happened.

42
00:03:49,640 --> 00:03:50,320
What do you mean?

43
00:03:52,400 --> 00:03:53,040
You see,

44
00:03:53,640 --> 00:03:55,720
I'm sure everyone has erred
when they were young.

45
00:03:55,920 --> 00:03:56,920
If a dog bites you,

46
00:03:57,000 --> 00:03:58,040
would you bite it back?

47
00:03:58,560 --> 00:04:00,520
Let's treat it
as if nothing had happened.

48
00:04:03,320 --> 00:04:03,840
A dog?

49
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:06,440
Bitten by a dog?

50
00:04:08,360 --> 00:04:09,640
I know my example

51
00:04:09,680 --> 00:04:10,555
is a little extreme.

52
00:04:10,666 --> 00:04:11,822
But it has the same meaning.

53
00:04:11,844 --> 00:04:13,360
It's good as long as you understand it.

54
00:04:13,400 --> 00:04:15,790
Just consider it as a mistake
that everyone makes, made by me

55
00:04:15,790 --> 00:04:17,711
when I was young
and didn't know any better.

56
00:04:18,480 --> 00:04:19,960
If you can't get over it...

57
00:04:20,040 --> 00:04:21,755
I've never thought of it as a thing!

58
00:04:24,560 --> 00:04:25,120
Really?

59
00:04:45,560 --> 00:04:46,080
Get out.

60
00:04:56,466 --> 00:04:58,080
Bitten by a dog? Do I look like a dog?

61
00:04:59,160 --> 00:05:00,400
Were you calling for me?

62
00:05:06,920 --> 00:05:07,440
Get out.

63
00:05:08,480 --> 00:05:09,160
Okay, Boss.

64
00:05:20,560 --> 00:05:21,960
Regarding our online event,

65
00:05:22,044 --> 00:05:23,444
which is to submit a vlog

66
00:05:23,466 --> 00:05:25,040
and win a luxury ocean-view suite,

67
00:05:25,600 --> 00:05:26,400
it has received

68
00:05:26,560 --> 00:05:27,920
over 1,000 vlogs.

69
00:05:28,088 --> 00:05:30,000
The Housekeeping Department
has to review them

70
00:05:30,280 --> 00:05:31,520
and choose the best one.

71
00:05:32,240 --> 00:05:33,280
Is there any volunteer?

72
00:05:36,400 --> 00:05:37,240
Isn't this the duty

73
00:05:37,480 --> 00:05:39,080
of the Publicity Department?

74
00:05:40,160 --> 00:05:41,640
I heard that the Publicity Department

75
00:05:41,760 --> 00:05:43,200
is getting ready for a huge event.

76
00:05:43,600 --> 00:05:45,280
They have no time for this.

77
00:05:45,480 --> 00:05:47,480
No days off? Not even a bonus?

78
00:05:47,733 --> 00:05:49,733
(Not me. Don't pick me)
No one's willing to do this.

79
00:05:49,755 --> 00:05:50,320
Precisely.

80
00:05:51,160 --> 00:05:51,880
Not me.

81
00:05:51,880 --> 00:05:53,240
(Rabbit, fried egg, ramen)

82
00:05:54,280 --> 00:05:54,680
Yi Ran.

83
00:05:58,777 --> 00:05:59,666
You shall do it.

84
00:06:00,920 --> 00:06:02,560
This can't be.

85
00:06:18,520 --> 00:06:19,320
Yi Ran,

86
00:06:20,080 --> 00:06:21,800
hurry and rest.

87
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:24,360
Your body can't take it
if you keep pulling all-nighters.

88
00:06:25,280 --> 00:06:26,840
I'm sure he's pranking me.

89
00:06:27,600 --> 00:06:29,040
He said the vlogs were short.

90
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:31,360
But each is around 20 minutes long.

91
00:06:32,520 --> 00:06:35,200
What have you done to offend him again?

92
00:06:36,240 --> 00:06:38,320
I blacked out.

93
00:06:38,377 --> 00:06:40,177
I ordered him around
for the entire night.

94
00:06:41,240 --> 00:06:42,960
But we've already
clarified the situation.

95
00:06:43,120 --> 00:06:44,320
We're even now.

96
00:06:44,320 --> 00:06:46,490
We were supposed to treat it
as if nothing had happened.

97
00:06:46,800 --> 00:06:49,640
Are you sure it's as simple
as ordering him around

98
00:06:49,640 --> 00:06:50,520
for the entire night?

99
00:06:51,440 --> 00:06:53,000
You blacked out, you know?

100
00:06:53,240 --> 00:06:54,977
How could you remember what you've done?

101
00:06:55,160 --> 00:06:56,440
That's what they said.

102
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:59,640
What you hear might not be true.
Seeing is believing.

103
00:07:00,040 --> 00:07:01,240
Maybe you've done something

104
00:07:01,280 --> 00:07:02,955
to make him hold a grudge against you.

105
00:07:03,800 --> 00:07:04,400
You're right.

106
00:07:04,777 --> 00:07:06,911
If I must die, I need to die
after knowing the truth.

107
00:07:16,120 --> 00:07:16,680
Who's there?

108
00:07:22,520 --> 00:07:24,120
No. You can't just access our footage

109
00:07:24,200 --> 00:07:25,040
casually.

110
00:07:25,480 --> 00:07:26,320
I know that.

111
00:07:27,711 --> 00:07:29,680
You said you wanted
to use the restroom, right?

112
00:07:30,422 --> 00:07:31,760
No matter how strict the hotel is,

113
00:07:31,760 --> 00:07:33,688
I'm sure you're allowed
to use the restroom.

114
00:07:33,711 --> 00:07:35,100
I'll go and use the restroom, then.

115
00:07:35,100 --> 00:07:36,822
I'll leave after putting
the drinks here.

116
00:07:36,920 --> 00:07:37,960
You better be quick.

117
00:07:47,460 --> 00:07:55,220
(Elevator)

118
00:07:58,400 --> 00:07:58,960
I...

119
00:07:59,040 --> 00:08:00,440
I should be in the restroom.

120
00:08:00,600 --> 00:08:01,960
I saw nothing.

121
00:08:15,460 --> 00:08:18,660
(Elevator, Thursday)

122
00:08:26,460 --> 00:08:29,540
=The Quirky and The Charming=

123
00:08:37,244 --> 00:08:38,680
You forgot to press the floor button.

124
00:08:44,977 --> 00:08:46,133
Did you do it on purpose?

125
00:08:47,840 --> 00:08:48,440
Yes.

126
00:08:49,040 --> 00:08:50,440
Regarding last night,

127
00:08:50,688 --> 00:08:52,533
(just treat it
as if nothing had happened.)

128
00:08:52,960 --> 00:08:55,000
I'm sure everyone has erred
when they were young.

129
00:08:55,240 --> 00:08:56,200
If a dog bites you,

130
00:08:56,320 --> 00:08:57,360
would you bite it back?

131
00:09:04,320 --> 00:09:06,000
I can't believe I made that comparison.

132
00:09:08,600 --> 00:09:10,000
Why exactly did he kiss me?

133
00:09:12,600 --> 00:09:13,720
You don't say?

134
00:09:14,200 --> 00:09:16,160
Of course it's because he fancies you.

135
00:09:17,600 --> 00:09:19,280
That's too sudden.

136
00:09:20,200 --> 00:09:22,240
I'm not prepared for this at all.

137
00:09:24,720 --> 00:09:27,440
Love comes too fast, just like a storm.

138
00:09:28,320 --> 00:09:30,440
Don't let happiness wait for too long.

139
00:09:31,200 --> 00:09:31,920
This won't do.

140
00:09:32,600 --> 00:09:34,120
He hasn't confessed to me yet.

141
00:09:35,440 --> 00:09:36,080
Yi Ran,

142
00:09:36,480 --> 00:09:38,520
since when were you this wishy-washy?

143
00:09:38,622 --> 00:09:40,533
Do you expect him
to wrap himself in a gift

144
00:09:40,577 --> 00:09:42,133
and deliver himself to your room?

145
00:09:46,320 --> 00:09:48,040
That'll do too.

146
00:09:53,480 --> 00:09:53,960
No.

147
00:09:54,440 --> 00:09:55,840
I have to clarify things with him.

148
00:10:13,920 --> 00:10:15,680
She's begging for forgiveness already.

149
00:10:17,320 --> 00:10:17,840
Fine.

150
00:10:18,640 --> 00:10:20,320
I'll give you one more chance.

151
00:10:24,000 --> 00:10:24,440
Hello?

152
00:10:25,480 --> 00:10:26,120
This won't do.

153
00:10:26,640 --> 00:10:28,320
I haven't figured out what to say yet.

154
00:10:37,240 --> 00:10:38,200
What should I do?

155
00:10:38,360 --> 00:10:38,680
I...

156
00:10:42,920 --> 00:10:44,666
The number you have dialed
is switched off.

157
00:10:44,666 --> 00:10:45,755
She switched her phone off?

158
00:10:48,920 --> 00:10:49,520
How dare you?

159
00:10:49,520 --> 00:10:51,320
Hello. The number you have dialed is...

160
00:11:28,480 --> 00:11:29,040
Hello?

161
00:11:30,422 --> 00:11:31,666
Join me for a boxing session.

162
00:11:31,960 --> 00:11:33,680
See you at the yoga studio
in half an hour.

163
00:11:34,200 --> 00:11:34,840
Boss,

164
00:11:35,040 --> 00:11:36,400
why don't we go somewhere else?

165
00:11:36,440 --> 00:11:37,080
Hello?

166
00:11:47,200 --> 00:11:47,640
Mr. Yan.

167
00:11:49,760 --> 00:11:51,320
This is an opportunity for you.

168
00:11:51,488 --> 00:11:53,000
Why don't you head to the yoga studio

169
00:11:53,000 --> 00:11:54,511
and have a deep conversation with Boss?

170
00:11:54,640 --> 00:11:55,320
Sure.

171
00:11:55,800 --> 00:11:57,680
Yoga is my expertise.

172
00:12:00,520 --> 00:12:03,040
If so, you have to perform well tonight.

173
00:12:29,840 --> 00:12:32,480
Are we never going
to see each other again?

174
00:12:32,800 --> 00:12:34,520
That won't be. Wait for me.

175
00:12:34,640 --> 00:12:36,800
I'll definitely come back and find you.

176
00:12:37,280 --> 00:12:38,320
Pinky promise.

177
00:12:38,600 --> 00:12:40,880
No. Only children do that.

178
00:12:40,920 --> 00:12:43,320
I'm leaving soon. Come on.

179
00:12:43,600 --> 00:12:44,520
Alright, then.

180
00:12:57,360 --> 00:12:58,120
Hello?

181
00:12:59,440 --> 00:13:00,280
Tiny Yi.

182
00:13:01,080 --> 00:13:02,320
Tell me.

183
00:13:04,560 --> 00:13:07,360
Is my return too late?

184
00:13:23,488 --> 00:13:24,711
Give me the same drink.

185
00:13:28,080 --> 00:13:31,360
Ms. Ling, you can't sleep
because of your loneliness either, huh?

186
00:13:32,288 --> 00:13:34,040
Are you trying to
drown yourself in sorrow?

187
00:13:40,540 --> 00:13:42,740
(Phone Call, Mr. Lin Jr.)

188
00:13:49,400 --> 00:13:50,280
Sorry about that.

189
00:13:51,444 --> 00:13:52,600
I called the wrong number.

190
00:13:54,360 --> 00:13:56,000
Yi Ran would never find out

191
00:13:56,000 --> 00:13:57,688
even if you drink
yourself to death here.

192
00:13:57,800 --> 00:13:59,520
If you like her,
you should fight for her.

193
00:14:01,920 --> 00:14:02,720
You're right.

194
00:14:04,640 --> 00:14:06,240
Hyenas can outdo lions

195
00:14:06,720 --> 00:14:10,080
if they work together.

196
00:14:10,560 --> 00:14:12,200
This isn't about me alone.

197
00:14:13,800 --> 00:14:15,400
If I lose to Xiao Mucheng,

198
00:14:16,560 --> 00:14:17,960
you'll lose to Yi Ran as well.

199
00:14:32,080 --> 00:14:33,920
I never worry about losing.

200
00:14:34,920 --> 00:14:36,520
But since you've already begged me,

201
00:14:36,911 --> 00:14:39,244
I guess I have no choice
but to agree to your request.

202
00:14:40,280 --> 00:14:40,840
Pinky promise.

203
00:14:43,120 --> 00:14:44,200
So childish.

204
00:14:56,400 --> 00:14:59,640
"Take things easy,
and life will be a breeze?"

205
00:15:00,360 --> 00:15:02,960
Is this an official announcement?

206
00:15:04,760 --> 00:15:06,160
How could you tell?

207
00:15:06,880 --> 00:15:08,000
Isn't it obvious?

208
00:15:08,800 --> 00:15:10,280
They drank together last night.

209
00:15:10,333 --> 00:15:11,720
And, they stayed out all night.

210
00:15:22,800 --> 00:15:24,240
Stop poking it.

211
00:15:24,400 --> 00:15:25,840
The rice will be ruined.

212
00:15:26,640 --> 00:15:29,120
No wonder you were upset
for the past few days.

213
00:15:29,640 --> 00:15:32,400
So, Yi Ran was the benchwarmer.

214
00:15:38,240 --> 00:15:39,680
The world of the rich

215
00:15:40,000 --> 00:15:41,400
isn't one we can just walk into.

216
00:15:41,680 --> 00:15:42,960
Don't give up easily.

217
00:15:43,480 --> 00:15:44,560
We still stand a chance.

218
00:15:45,440 --> 00:15:48,800
Why don't we join hands

219
00:15:49,040 --> 00:15:50,440
and separate them?

220
00:15:50,840 --> 00:15:53,000
(If a dog bites you,
would you bite it back?)

221
00:15:53,480 --> 00:15:55,440
Let's treat it
as if nothing had happened.

222
00:15:56,000 --> 00:15:58,280
Why do you look happy all of a sudden?

223
00:15:58,680 --> 00:15:59,800
What's the matter?

224
00:16:00,320 --> 00:16:01,560
Who said I looked happy?

225
00:16:01,920 --> 00:16:04,840
I just feel heartbroken
and upset for Yi Ran.

226
00:16:09,840 --> 00:16:10,560
I'm full.

227
00:16:11,280 --> 00:16:12,320
You guys can go ahead.

228
00:16:13,000 --> 00:16:14,360
You haven't even taken a bite.

229
00:16:15,640 --> 00:16:16,440
Let her be.

230
00:16:16,960 --> 00:16:18,800
She needs some time alone.

231
00:16:40,360 --> 00:16:40,960
Mr. Yan.

232
00:16:41,355 --> 00:16:42,244
What a coincidence.

233
00:16:43,760 --> 00:16:45,120
What do you want for lunch today?

234
00:16:45,680 --> 00:16:46,960
Order away. It's my treat.

235
00:16:49,844 --> 00:16:51,133
I want to eat someone alive.

236
00:16:53,240 --> 00:16:54,720
I thought of you as a brother.

237
00:16:55,640 --> 00:16:57,240
But you took me as a fool, huh?

238
00:16:58,240 --> 00:16:59,800
You said you gave me an opportunity

239
00:16:59,800 --> 00:17:01,520
to engage in
a deep conversation with him.

240
00:17:01,960 --> 00:17:02,920
Look at my eyes!

241
00:17:06,400 --> 00:17:07,577
Are the bruises deep enough?

242
00:17:11,280 --> 00:17:11,760
Mr. Yan.

243
00:17:12,320 --> 00:17:14,840
Why don't you let me explain myself?

244
00:17:15,000 --> 00:17:15,640
No, I won't!

245
00:17:16,920 --> 00:17:18,760
You see, at that moment,

246
00:17:19,120 --> 00:17:19,720
I was...

247
00:17:20,240 --> 00:17:21,920
What are you two doing here?

248
00:17:24,280 --> 00:17:26,640
Nothing. It was just a casual chat.

249
00:17:28,320 --> 00:17:30,240
I told you to stop, right? Does it hurt?

250
00:17:31,960 --> 00:17:32,640
I'm fine.

251
00:17:33,280 --> 00:17:33,920
Say,

252
00:17:34,360 --> 00:17:35,800
after our boxing session last night,

253
00:17:36,160 --> 00:17:37,880
I feel great today.

254
00:17:37,955 --> 00:17:39,333
I have to learn more from you.

255
00:17:40,160 --> 00:17:42,000
Sure. Let's have another session

256
00:17:42,520 --> 00:17:43,520
tonight.

257
00:17:44,888 --> 00:17:46,533
Chen Mo, you should join us too.

258
00:17:58,160 --> 00:17:58,840
Let's go!

259
00:18:04,600 --> 00:18:05,040
Come in.

260
00:18:19,320 --> 00:18:20,320
So...

261
00:18:20,488 --> 00:18:21,822
Have you selected the best vlog?

262
00:18:22,040 --> 00:18:23,000
Not yet.

263
00:18:24,120 --> 00:18:26,200
That night...

264
00:18:27,111 --> 00:18:29,688
Why are you standing here
when you haven't finished your task?

265
00:18:29,822 --> 00:18:30,888
Is there anything else?

266
00:18:34,311 --> 00:18:35,866
Now, you remember everything, huh?

267
00:18:36,680 --> 00:18:38,280
You irresponsible woman!

268
00:18:42,200 --> 00:18:42,920
I...

269
00:18:43,960 --> 00:18:45,760
Seems like you have
nothing important to say.

270
00:18:46,280 --> 00:18:47,120
I'm very busy now.

271
00:18:49,400 --> 00:18:50,760
Out with it!

272
00:18:58,822 --> 00:18:59,800
Are you truly leaving?

273
00:19:00,720 --> 00:19:01,800
Leave if you dare!

274
00:19:04,200 --> 00:19:05,040
She did leave.

275
00:19:05,555 --> 00:19:06,680
She even slammed the door?

276
00:19:13,400 --> 00:19:14,280
It was windy just now.

277
00:19:14,800 --> 00:19:16,600
I didn't mean to slam the door.

278
00:19:17,880 --> 00:19:18,440
Get out.

279
00:19:31,880 --> 00:19:33,640
