364
00:23:27,280 --> 00:23:28,840
and let me remain until now.

365
00:23:29,760 --> 00:23:32,080
I'm very grateful to him.

366
00:23:34,511 --> 00:23:35,600
Don't just stare into space.

367
00:23:35,600 --> 00:23:36,720
Come, let's drink.

368
00:23:46,640 --> 00:23:49,280
I hope you two can be reunited.

369
00:23:51,200 --> 00:23:53,280
This is what love should be like.

370
