how it feels to encounter love.

375
00:24:08,760 --> 00:24:11,320
Child, let me tell you something.

376
00:24:13,000 --> 00:24:15,120
If you meet someone

377
00:24:15,440 --> 00:24:17,760
who makes you
think about him unconsciously...

378
00:24:18,880 --> 00:24:20,760
No matter if you're happy, upset,

379
00:24:21,120 --> 00:24:22,600
