396
00:26:01,160 --> 00:26:02,422
Hello. I've made a reservation.

397
00:26:02,640 --> 00:26:03,400
Hello, Miss Bei.

398
00:26:03,600 --> 00:26:05,200
Welcome to Spring Sea Resort Hotel.

399
00:26:05,720 --> 00:26:06,760
I'm a fan of yours.

400
00:26:06,760 --> 00:26:08,040
I've been following your channel.

401
00:26:08,120 --> 00:26:08,600
Thank you.

402
00:26:09,600 --> 00:26:11,400
Are you a Sagittarius?

403
00:26:12,200 --> 00:26:13,240
How did you find out?

404
00:26:13,720 --> 00:26:14,480
That's amazing.

405
00:26:14,840 --> 00:26:16,320
You look like someone proud

406
00:26:16,520 --> 00:26:17,600
and highly capable.

407
00:26:17,777 --> 00:26:20,160
Right now, the stars have arrived in
your Five Orientations,

408
00:26:20,400 --> 00:26:21,880
and Mercury is about to join them.

409
00:26:22,000 --> 00:26:24,290
