427
00:27:13,280 --> 00:27:15,044
If too many,
move to the Executive Lounge.

428
00:27:15,120 --> 00:27:15,520
Okay.

429
00:27:17,088 --> 00:27:17,933
By the way,

430
00:27:18,133 --> 00:27:19,920
I didn't see Yi Ran today. Where is she?

431
00:27:20,640 --> 00:27:22,120
