432
00:27:22,720 --> 00:27:23,560
Again?

433
00:27:23,840 --> 00:27:26,040
You yourself said
that she could take a paid leave.

434
00:27:26,111 --> 00:27:28,022
I think she's reviewing
the vlogs as we speak.

435
00:27:28,111 --> 00:27:30,066
