the same thing with them.

447
00:28:10,155 --> 00:28:11,777
Do you need me to lend you a hand?

448
00:28:11,911 --> 00:28:13,155
Here's my advice for you.

449
00:28:13,480 --> 00:28:15,080
Beisiman is no ordinary company.

450
00:28:15,240 --> 00:28:16,880
You guys should keep an eye on them.

451
00:28:18,080 --> 00:28:19,200
Are you worried about me?

452
00:28:21,080 --> 00:28:22,000
Don't worry.

453
00:28:22,080 --> 00:28:23,888
