474
00:29:33,480 --> 00:29:35,080
Did you confess to her or not?

475
00:29:36,480 --> 00:29:37,520
If this keeps up,

476
00:29:37,640 --> 00:29:38,760
you'll lose her.

477
00:29:39,200 --> 00:29:40,800
I think you misunderstood something.

478
00:29:42,480 --> 00:29:43,160
Waiter.

479
00:29:49,680 --> 00:29:50,160
