480
00:29:52,622 --> 00:29:55,149
Sweet and Sour Pork Ribs,
Sweet and Sour Pork Fillet,

481
00:29:55,150 --> 00:29:56,380
Pineapple Sweet and Sour Pork,

482
00:29:56,644 --> 00:29:57,666
Honey Glazed Char Siu.

483
00:29:58,133 --> 00:29:59,866
Tiny Yi loved sweet food since young.

484
00:29:59,888 --> 00:30:02,960
