I'm allergic to pollen,

553
00:34:07,120 --> 00:34:09,280
but I don't want to let my fans down.

554
00:34:10,360 --> 00:34:10,880
Understood.

555
00:34:10,880 --> 00:34:13,777
But these will affect the other guests
if you leave them in the corridor.

556
00:34:13,844 --> 00:34:14,529
What about this?

557
00:34:14,530 --> 00:34:15,760
Please give me an address.

558
00:34:15,800 --> 00:34:17,040
I'll deliver them to your house.

559
00:34:18,360 --> 00:34:19,360
Sorry for the trouble.

560
00:34:19,680 --> 00:34:21,280
You have to do this because of me.

561
00:34:21,422 --> 00:34:22,160
Sorry about this.

562
00:34:22,840 --> 00:34:23,360
It's my duty.

563
00:34:23,577 --> 00:34:24,600
If you need anything,

564
00:34:24,680 --> 00:34:25,840
you may find us at any time.

565
00:34:26,222 --> 00:34:27,333
Sorry for the interruption.

566
00:34:28,000 --> 00:34:28,640
Wait.

567
00:34:29,240 --> 00:34:30,920
One of my earrings is missing.

568
00:34:31,000 --> 00:34:32,600
Can you please find it for me?

569
00:34:34,680 --> 00:34:35,160
Okay.

570
00:34:49,800 --> 00:34:51,240
It should be around this area.

571
00:34:52,720 --> 00:34:54,640
It's a white pearl earring.

572
00:35:00,000 --> 00:35:01,400
Miss Bei, what are you doing?

573
00:35:01,720 --> 00:35:02,280
Miss Bei!

574
00:35:02,488 --> 00:35:03,400
Please let me hug you.

575
00:35:03,520 --> 00:35:05,040
Just one minute!

576
00:35:05,066 --> 00:35:05,880
Miss Bei, I'm sorry.

577
00:35:05,960 --> 00:35:06,680
Please let go.

578
00:35:07,040 --> 00:35:07,600
Miss Bei!

579
00:35:08,555 --> 00:35:10,422
- Miss Bei, please let go.
- Let him go!

580
00:35:14,430 --> 00:35:15,530
Action.

581
00:35:19,240 --> 00:35:20,300
It's such a coincidence.

582
00:35:21,088 --> 00:35:22,288
Why don't we share a table?

583
00:35:27,830 --> 00:35:28,710
Are you truly leaving?

584
00:35:28,710 --> 00:35:29,920
Leave if you dare!

585
00:35:30,190 --> 00:35:31,540
Out with it.

586
00:35:33,533 --> 00:35:34,730
No matter how similar it looks,

587
00:35:34,730 --> 00:35:36,420
you can't just touch it like that.

588
00:35:38,130 --> 00:35:39,200
Say it.

589
00:35:41,400 --> 00:35:42,310
Action.

590
00:35:44,160 --> 00:35:49,160
=The Quirky and The Charming=
